-{"id":"asupersync-1sk16w.7","title":"[phase-1][http] Add indexed trailer HeaderMap lookup backing","description":"Bounded Phase-1 follow-up for the open stub tracker. Scope: src/http/body.rs only. Keep the existing HeaderMap API and trailer iteration order, but add an internal indexed lookup path so get()/insert()/append() no longer depend solely on linear scans over the backing Vec. Preserve deterministic behavior, duplicate-header semantics for append(), and inline tests in the same file. Validate with rch-backed targeted cargo commands and update Agent Mail + beads as progress lands.","status":"in_progress","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"CopperBear","created_at":"2026-03-27T05:14:20.537954358Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-27T05:14:20.537954358Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["http","phase-1","trailers"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1sk16w.7","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1sk16w","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-27T05:14:20.537954358Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
