 {"id":"asupersync-1sk16w.8","title":"[REMOTE] Make RemoteHandle abort send protocol cancel requests","description":"`src/remote.rs` documents `RemoteHandle::abort()` as the request path for remote cancellation, but the method is still a Phase-0 no-op even when a real `RemoteRuntime` is attached via `RemoteCap`.

Scope:
